{"tid":714824,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"哈薩克12日遊 - 六月最好時光","createTime":"2018-06-24T02:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T09:30:45.000Z","uid":84581,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"225856de03e06dcefb1410436d09403d8289ca25","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"好啦，我以前外國intern果陣識左幾個哈薩克朋友，佢地之前黎左香港探我，咁我就禮貌上去番佢地國家探佢地，如果唔係我諗我十年內都冇諗過去呢個地方。哈薩克有大自然景點要包車或報local tour，但tour時間大多都係weekend，所以路線編排由Almalty（Lake）  &gt; Shymkent &gt; Turkestan &gt; Almalty （Canyon）。<br />\n<br />\nAir Astana每星期都會有兩班由香港去almarty既航機 （阿拉木圖，第二大城市，亦係我朋友住既地方）。雖然Air Astana既機比較細，但裡面好靚好舒服，空服service都好好，仲不停派禮物野食野飲，好開心。（我班係morning flight，佢地會派酒派vodka，果然深受俄羅斯影響）<br />\n飛機下降見到雪山真係好靚，六月係哈薩克最美時光，雪山仲未溶雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104727_be39d6e3949058e712b7cc0700c28af2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104727_be39d6e3949058e712b7cc0700c28af2.JPG&h=68d0d554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機之後，我同友人接受佢地機埸訪問關於佢地條輸送帶好唔好，我地見慣香港機埸果條梗覺得小巫見大巫啦，不果都禮貌讚下okay okay。<br />\n<br />\n好多人對哈薩克感覺都係落後，undeveloped，但其實大地市唔算太差，有d似歐洲，加上比雪山圍嬈，令我諗起以前係奧地利既時光，不愧人稱&ldquo;亞洲瑞士&rdquo;。 街好大好闊，餐廳大多都好大好大好大，裝修好靚價錢唔貴，簡直係香港人一直追求既享受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104935_ede93e2f2ca283bf2aa5e30c982ece01.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104935_ede93e2f2ca283bf2aa5e30c982ece01.JPG&h=e6c13ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104937_0ebb26fd0b3c46bb9d7a93c992743cd5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104937_0ebb26fd0b3c46bb9d7a93c992743cd5.JPG&h=9f47e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104939_9080f86b0ca091db81f53877fded62d4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104939_9080f86b0ca091db81f53877fded62d4.JPG&h=58cd10c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104940_eb49b147cab0559332596fd613f0af18.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104940_eb49b147cab0559332596fd613f0af18.JPG&h=ee8a06ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104942_e9e19f2d9333d2f2790f1457ea8f9964.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104942_e9e19f2d9333d2f2790f1457ea8f9964.JPG&h=e6ba20eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104944_a6a5f5899a069b9cffcb5859c282e63c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104944_a6a5f5899a069b9cffcb5859c282e63c.JPG&h=c097a28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/104945_8a1524ee3bf89bfd4c651d62aa53b735.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F104945_8a1524ee3bf89bfd4c651d62aa53b735.JPG&h=1e43a79f&s={SIZE}\" /> Opera house<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105117_be4238c36c04c59727dd65451c8b4d9b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105117_be4238c36c04c59727dd65451c8b4d9b.JPG&h=174034ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105119_134892ede8d4c4254bd91800ad9eee40.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105119_134892ede8d4c4254bd91800ad9eee40.JPG&h=c1185ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105120_61985651254312d4fb8fa6a5425412eb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105120_61985651254312d4fb8fa6a5425412eb.JPG&h=95816e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有d似香港既唐樓，但佢地會mix唔同建築物料，外牆石屎，木，磚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105236_57f0780bb05179192dc9a746d91cb72a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105236_57f0780bb05179192dc9a746d91cb72a.JPG&h=6d35d6f2&s={SIZE}\" /> 街邊都有好多偉人雕像<br />\n<br />\n第一晚去左一間叫RUMI既餐廳，我想講相片係表達唔到有幾靚&hellip;&hellip;事前係Trip Advisor睇好似平平無奇，但親眼見到過下真係心花怒放，好異國風情、色彩班爛、周圍都係馬賽克<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105322_ecca9699df4448409bbe48c42e760e39.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105322_ecca9699df4448409bbe48c42e760e39.JPG&h=133fbaaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105324_db3baa1d6b3e1e07c5a576b69ea97552.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105324_db3baa1d6b3e1e07c5a576b69ea97552.JPG&h=29b8190e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105325_de6abecfe8e6b76a0596971ca34c5212.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105325_de6abecfe8e6b76a0596971ca34c5212.JPG&h=4c645614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105344_08e8b56d489e5ef4d8c5b87e628a6568.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105344_08e8b56d489e5ef4d8c5b87e628a6568.JPG&h=a133d9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nManti （餃子），手抓飯，warm salad （佢地好喜歡暖的沙律）。正確黎講，佢地本土National food好少，呢到好多國家性食物其實係源自 吉爾吉斯斯坦（ kyrgyzstan），例如我地覺得出自新彊既手抓飯。<br />\n<br />\n值得一講係，現時呢度既物價對港紙係偏低，物價大約係港紙1／4，好似晚餐一個手抓飯大約hkd＄30，一杯咖啡大約hkd＄16。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105441_176eef1e9f112afdd402019371849739.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105441_176eef1e9f112afdd402019371849739.JPG&h=2a229b15&s={SIZE}\" />馬肉乾 ＋牛肉乾，我唔太好馬肉，可能係習慣問題，大部份時間都係友人食馬肉"},{"pid":"84f2db7780aed0bb303c8a509e66a462ce297ee7","tid":714824,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"值得一講係，現時呢度既物價對港紙係偏低，物價大約係港紙1／4，好似晚餐一個手抓飯大約hkd＄30，一杯咖啡大約hkd＄16。<br />\n<br />\n咁都叫 四分一 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478efc96d827b35465cf72639b1c95f90ebd249e","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105623_a8e0e77b9d3edbe1f8cfbc59ace711a3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105623_a8e0e77b9d3edbe1f8cfbc59ace711a3.JPG&h=52795eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二日去左Green Market，一個好local 既街市。雖然係街市，但好整理同乾淨，即使賣肉個部份都唔會有異味同血淋淋。其實街市唔比影相，所以我只係快快影左幾張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105707_20289c060d936c1e4014264f54157945.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105707_20289c060d936c1e4014264f54157945.JPG&h=369a648b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105708_3f26b3546c6380d9be117cdc9abdde1e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105708_3f26b3546c6380d9be117cdc9abdde1e.JPG&h=4e0171d0&s={SIZE}\" /> 有新鮮馬肉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105710_f95446764bd033efa2ad98a794889d9c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105710_f95446764bd033efa2ad98a794889d9c.JPG&h=5bd5f808&s={SIZE}\" /> 乾果仲會比你試食<br />\n<br />\n跟完行左會附近一個好大既公園 Gorky Park，都係好大好大好大都有個怪怪恐龍館<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/105804_47d5526490068935816ce0f0bc7b891b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F105804_47d5526490068935816ce0f0bc7b891b.JPG&h=38ac1073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地d公園會有機動遊戲，由過山車，bb跳樓機，乜都有&hellip;但我係見唔到有人玩既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110001_211ed6d9242e36c8db9f8f71192d530a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110001_211ed6d9242e36c8db9f8f71192d530a.JPG&h=de86ee19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110003_4b0edfcf4a1aba4e3578dc370cac1cda.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110003_4b0edfcf4a1aba4e3578dc370cac1cda.JPG&h=9b25d432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110004_f29e5afdeab475de012bafda680a9907.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110004_f29e5afdeab475de012bafda680a9907.JPG&h=598ff4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110008_7f9a33bc6d1a1af7e7109f1d9f014e67.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110008_7f9a33bc6d1a1af7e7109f1d9f014e67.JPG&h=9f314639&s={SIZE}\" /> 水族館<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110010_d507e33e53029bda451a25ef6ad86ad5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110010_d507e33e53029bda451a25ef6ad86ad5.JPG&h=f8a4d976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110011_5fbf097ff45cb3ff097b955b47e4b5bf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110011_5fbf097ff45cb3ff097b955b47e4b5bf.JPG&h=52c27595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110104_d790d310a25ef09ca9dfc2433702b808.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110104_d790d310a25ef09ca9dfc2433702b808.JPG&h=b5b3659e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110105_2a0393ef0b6d543c9b14d2976ccfd1c5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110105_2a0393ef0b6d543c9b14d2976ccfd1c5.JPG&h=5bb4a3e3&s={SIZE}\" /> 蘇聯式樓宇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110107_7a824d5ebac79f0a4dc523b5965fff52.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110107_7a824d5ebac79f0a4dc523b5965fff52.JPG&h=5f3599ae&s={SIZE}\" /> 媽好感動，係哈迪斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110149_3c2440988b4ddbaee11ca773b2aced5f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110149_3c2440988b4ddbaee11ca773b2aced5f.JPG&h=8ad40bf0&s={SIZE}\" /> 一心諗住睇佢地好峴名既東正教教堂，點知維修緊<br />\n<br />\n紀念戰爭士兵像同火炬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110221_a4962695dc142d27a39b6d25fc469316.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110221_a4962695dc142d27a39b6d25fc469316.JPG&h=9dd7648b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110223_8353ee220cf66a513506f0ee8c2d955a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110223_8353ee220cf66a513506f0ee8c2d955a.JPG&h=00dc917d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110225_606fa3befddfbf65324c8f41528df427.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110225_606fa3befddfbf65324c8f41528df427.JPG&h=74ac522f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110302_9a9d4191940ac2dcb4b20c4e9bc7596a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110302_9a9d4191940ac2dcb4b20c4e9bc7596a.JPG&h=50b4e111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110304_360784a06058c7b9e1f0fce4206b444c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110304_360784a06058c7b9e1f0fce4206b444c.JPG&h=3386d0bd&s={SIZE}\" /> 沿路行都會見到雪山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110331_7d6072decb463bc18f6e93a87711933a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110331_7d6072decb463bc18f6e93a87711933a.JPG&h=48a61c62&s={SIZE}\" /> 下午去左當地既National Museum，外表幾靚幾宏偉，但裡面就&hellip;&hellip;展品唔太多，但哈薩克文同俄文，所以普通行左下就走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110357_3b01b7f5cdc21729690ebcbfa746ee1a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110357_3b01b7f5cdc21729690ebcbfa746ee1a.JPG&h=142c823d&s={SIZE}\" /> 國家出土既長毛象骨頭，處理安置手法好有性格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110435_fcfa34043ec4d7e3bbf16e487e997307.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110435_fcfa34043ec4d7e3bbf16e487e997307.JPG&h=64e689e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110436_3b12d52c82bfd7a0596b795684d728fc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110436_3b12d52c82bfd7a0596b795684d728fc.JPG&h=6ac5064d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110437_2e1d150855b05790396dfc376cbbdc08.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110437_2e1d150855b05790396dfc376cbbdc08.JPG&h=c787e60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係supermarket買左駱駝奶同馬奶，難飲都面容扭曲。事後我同哈薩克朋友〝投訴〞，佢地話冇理由好delicious佢地好鐘意，仲叫我market買新鮮既，新鮮既真係好好飲，馬奶亦成為我之後旅程早餐必飲。"},{"pid":"c30a3dd9810036dc691d6d64d53c4fb48dd75115","tid":714824,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"直接貼女啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47668122998999d89430f166ce58f2909b99358e","tid":714824,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:09:44.000Z","msg":"劉明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0753d062a43f34fce449f4b915a6054e19da2ff","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"第三日，我地未出發前已經物色好local tour去睇湖，Big Almalty Lake。<br />\n點解個湖可以有Tiffany Blue既顏色咁靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110628_eee7425129adbeba237fa049745e1bba.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110628_eee7425129adbeba237fa049745e1bba.JPG&h=74198e34&s={SIZE}\" /> 沿路以為自己身在瑞士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110654_ecf3a756abbcf3b037dd3f0a3c456dcd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110654_ecf3a756abbcf3b037dd3f0a3c456dcd.JPG&h=c93a2dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110658_e9a25caf1f9ce30b82dffa0c644ed1eb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110658_e9a25caf1f9ce30b82dffa0c644ed1eb.JPG&h=4ec25519&s={SIZE}\" /> 自己係香港都有行山，但呢種美景要用breathtaking形容，仙境一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110800_2da7c8afb26e8bde52f88aa93bfb5117.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110800_2da7c8afb26e8bde52f88aa93bfb5117.JPG&h=2d2814b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110802_3945e265e1fac994e216cc855e44d8cb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110802_3945e265e1fac994e216cc855e44d8cb.JPG&h=a23a9cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110804_0871a2c006591d31f733abbe9caa70fc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110804_0871a2c006591d31f733abbe9caa70fc.JPG&h=023cf4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110806_ee77f99f639cbdd7ad68917661ffb55f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110806_ee77f99f639cbdd7ad68917661ffb55f.JPG&h=6e315454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112559_a1fe299416394a51a41329e0873839c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112559_a1fe299416394a51a41329e0873839c6.png&h=d4d3af37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110812_318269d33a3b890bde7082d4109bcefd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110812_318269d33a3b890bde7082d4109bcefd.JPG&h=05feccef&s={SIZE}\" /> 郊外廁所，非常臭，就地解決會好d<br />\n<br />\n事後導遊都好好，車團友去睇附近既小瀑布（仲push我地行上瀑布，事前應該買重保險）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110919_d79877294c835a581c1e506fa65453bc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110919_d79877294c835a581c1e506fa65453bc.JPG&h=cb46e0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110921_65b16700cfb38b7f11b3681772ff9c87.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110921_65b16700cfb38b7f11b3681772ff9c87.JPG&h=eafe3061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/110923_77c3f12fdfccaf2828aec9e70e03fee8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F110923_77c3f12fdfccaf2828aec9e70e03fee8.JPG&h=2ca9ae61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖之後我地就搭內陸機另一個南部城市Shymkent，因為我地要去睇以前成吉思汗之地Turkestan。我地揀左內陸機SCAT，竟然突然delay八個鐘，安排左我地去flight crew酒店休息等。名義上係酒店，但感覺似我地烏溪沙度假村咁。 Almalty既城市圖上，雪山同景點大多於北邊，機埸係南邊。哈薩克朋友仔同我講愈有錢既人就住晒係北邊，南邊都係窮人（明白，好似我地香港聽人講住赤柱咁），於是我地趁呢個機會行出附近睇睇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111041_033366f02762c88d2370b85cc9713966.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111041_033366f02762c88d2370b85cc9713966.JPG&h=98d2fc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111043_0b02c9a95237754df7525c1f563ad420.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111043_0b02c9a95237754df7525c1f563ad420.JPG&h=9ee771eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111045_38907da3729587b4729026bc2ffd1e15.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111045_38907da3729587b4729026bc2ffd1e15.JPG&h=4ac7f0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111047_28ce5792cb01545b758dbd5f2f86f183.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111047_28ce5792cb01545b758dbd5f2f86f183.JPG&h=dc84ecd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111048_9cf6837eee0cff650bdaa0067067a949.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111048_9cf6837eee0cff650bdaa0067067a949.JPG&h=eb716da9&s={SIZE}\" /> 真係好荒漠，歐洲既境像完全消失，呢一部份真係附合香港人對哈薩克既印象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111050_6096cca421d70dfa2eacfe07ea4ab47d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111050_6096cca421d70dfa2eacfe07ea4ab47d.JPG&h=461aec22&s={SIZE}\" /> 肚餓啦，手指指篤住人地食緊乜老闆就明白了<br />\n<br />\n對於南部城市，我d哈薩克朋友好反對我去，話好危險唔好去，佢地城市人亦唔太喜歡呢個鄉下地方，覺得Shymkent d人好strerotype又粗魯（大慨同香港人睇部份大陸人差唔多）<br />\n<br />\nShymkent 呢個地方真係幾窮同落後，稍為靚少少既建築物都冇&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111227_420b455fd604ee23a3a1333ddbf165dc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111227_420b455fd604ee23a3a1333ddbf165dc.JPG&h=dd0ffb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111229_3892c5ce96150b8d48d0ec7ef49eb01a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111229_3892c5ce96150b8d48d0ec7ef49eb01a.JPG&h=886ad4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111230_d29ab90c723791c49836854588a671e1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111230_d29ab90c723791c49836854588a671e1.JPG&h=c0259bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111232_60ce080c9fca39d6d5da4c104f91fb99.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111232_60ce080c9fca39d6d5da4c104f91fb99.JPG&h=e01b100d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111233_2ce17198623b5f0d1c62bc9c69425cf9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111233_2ce17198623b5f0d1c62bc9c69425cf9.JPG&h=e61682a4&s={SIZE}\" /> 但政府d錢就用黎起個好大貌似宏偉既公園，但40度晒到濃幾可有人去公園&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111302_900d4f68c6c3d5694e9cfa3f022613e5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111302_900d4f68c6c3d5694e9cfa3f022613e5.JPG&h=cfdac40d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111303_f71d9569520690a8099222f6c91a8ecd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111303_f71d9569520690a8099222f6c91a8ecd.JPG&h=78871dc0&s={SIZE}\" /> 公園旁邊既清真寺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，我地去左個local 街市睇下d風土人情 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111424_e9fb5bbf891a85a359acf2b6ef452206.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111424_e9fb5bbf891a85a359acf2b6ef452206.JPG&h=20dd270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111425_7bd9c2c363d251f8065edba996c3a41f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111425_7bd9c2c363d251f8065edba996c3a41f.JPG&h=c277e5b8&s={SIZE}\" /> 唔比人影相我明，但唔比吹喇叭係咩意思<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111427_e2aec8c6397fb234b7d00f5af2092efd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111427_e2aec8c6397fb234b7d00f5af2092efd.JPG&h=0f8001de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111428_a87a15695cddbd9acf5c3c2b4ad26278.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111428_a87a15695cddbd9acf5c3c2b4ad26278.JPG&h=524a74e5&s={SIZE}\" /> 我都買左個食，大個我個頭，＄100等於hkd大約2蚊雞，真係又平又好食"},{"pid":"4b8b85f36453ce8626d32b3078489ed7d5ea1304","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"街市入面乜都有，由濕貨乾貨乜都擺埋一齊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111534_131803b0a41a93dbd1a5b3b30543d1fd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111534_131803b0a41a93dbd1a5b3b30543d1fd.JPG&h=df593df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111535_78c0bad018588ef58676e8d6c814e63c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111535_78c0bad018588ef58676e8d6c814e63c.JPG&h=f6d91f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111538_7a95e8739eedc6ac680dabe5308009da.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111538_7a95e8739eedc6ac680dabe5308009da.JPG&h=2fd7192f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111540_7f3724b80986365bcafb21cf188e9c8a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111540_7f3724b80986365bcafb21cf188e9c8a.JPG&h=bece5443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111541_f27df44962c12a3bc969fed3526eae9f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111541_f27df44962c12a3bc969fed3526eae9f.JPG&h=5ab1040e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111544_42f5fb75060a78359a73a4899c6cd508.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111544_42f5fb75060a78359a73a4899c6cd508.JPG&h=099416f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市內有個怪怪小公園，又係有怪怪機動遊戲同小動物<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111707_12fdb197fbb9eca756ec53f31ad044b0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111707_12fdb197fbb9eca756ec53f31ad044b0.JPG&h=b5d85e3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111709_d65ee099a27add0fd15b5544f865b1cf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111709_d65ee099a27add0fd15b5544f865b1cf.JPG&h=fa682fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111713_598f55f8e1be74f085ce3ff081a8afea.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111713_598f55f8e1be74f085ce3ff081a8afea.JPG&h=09e8b5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111715_8ca807e1f97a97624e512aa847708198.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111715_8ca807e1f97a97624e512aa847708198.JPG&h=859d0361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111717_69873fabc1f8b3aebf46f49569e7a17d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111717_69873fabc1f8b3aebf46f49569e7a17d.JPG&h=c8868013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111720_fe9896e69ca2c1e7ae396bc6208b8527.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111720_fe9896e69ca2c1e7ae396bc6208b8527.JPG&h=b4b6eaa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111722_57a3f955fe63f165facdcb1998c74d65.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111722_57a3f955fe63f165facdcb1998c74d65.JPG&h=53300467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111723_e20e218c5d9535d7fd707d4f60a53c8c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111723_e20e218c5d9535d7fd707d4f60a53c8c.JPG&h=af921aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111725_0802e69975761b82573a5dcc1ee237db.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111725_0802e69975761b82573a5dcc1ee237db.JPG&h=829ec02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111727_bf13122d051e2e009727c13bbda9c18d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111727_bf13122d051e2e009727c13bbda9c18d.JPG&h=0d270aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稍後就向酒店包左車去Turkestan，車程2.5小時，沿路都係一望無際既草原同沙漠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111828_c7ea9f97e398a2273698db6f06fb8fe9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111828_c7ea9f97e398a2273698db6f06fb8fe9.JPG&h=c4821a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/111831_9514f396c0f8723e412c3fb9bb8de026.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F111831_9514f396c0f8723e412c3fb9bb8de026.JPG&h=02f8e0b5&s={SIZE}\" /> 望住發覺自己更加渺小<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTurkestan係一個小鎮（差唔多阿富汗上面），因為成吉思汗同帖木兒出名，歷史唔講太多，怕講錯誤人子弟。全部都係爛身小房子，遊客更加稀小<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112034_9283f2d30f1fb26341b79fbb97f6a05e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112034_9283f2d30f1fb26341b79fbb97f6a05e.JPG&h=d381bc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112037_16854b7a36f1a9bb0b5352c46748c4ae.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112037_16854b7a36f1a9bb0b5352c46748c4ae.JPG&h=30e0a1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112039_cd75dac271b09c5e2c59a5387c94d634.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112039_cd75dac271b09c5e2c59a5387c94d634.JPG&h=1db60985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112041_38b55358ece246bf1eaae744a1609f3a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112041_38b55358ece246bf1eaae744a1609f3a.JPG&h=0f5e43b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112043_523eecbb8880612674fb1794b6800ca4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112043_523eecbb8880612674fb1794b6800ca4.JPG&h=8666ddf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出奇地有間專做遊客既餐廳，係到可以見晒黎Turkestan既遊客，因為個個都係黎呢到食飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112127_f7872acd32f798e508702743ca5c4134.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112127_f7872acd32f798e508702743ca5c4134.JPG&h=1a65f21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/112128_f181bcf3d07561ec23a7643dc2a47949.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F112128_f181bcf3d07561ec23a7643dc2a47949.JPG&h=5905561f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n休息一晚又出發，首先去最出名既Mausoleum of Khoja Ahmed Yasawi （當年帖木兒為一個宗教士建既陵墓）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113055_00fc22bb03c710d633deef15eb6632cb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113055_00fc22bb03c710d633deef15eb6632cb.JPG&h=3981e68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113058_627b19703d25ad1145125680fb4a31f7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113058_627b19703d25ad1145125680fb4a31f7.JPG&h=e26d8edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113100_3c14113b8a2be13a6b2e4692c1483e6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113100_3c14113b8a2be13a6b2e4692c1483e6a.JPG&h=0ce1302e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113102_455bed3e405a40bfd951c5f2517cfad9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113102_455bed3e405a40bfd951c5f2517cfad9.JPG&h=ad963912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113103_0a6df0902edf2f0c8dfbd04e6e96fd7a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113103_0a6df0902edf2f0c8dfbd04e6e96fd7a.JPG&h=3752c594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113104_51b0bde022de6f606ea8b528394bfa07.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113104_51b0bde022de6f606ea8b528394bfa07.JPG&h=4d0298b5&s={SIZE}\" /> 另外既小公主陵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113221_e057f98dac93dc8a2260484ef7995249.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113221_e057f98dac93dc8a2260484ef7995249.JPG&h=78269eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113222_e4bedf07b47f8860c9a3558a64d37a3d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113222_e4bedf07b47f8860c9a3558a64d37a3d.JPG&h=a0a911cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113225_e6111d249769c480546ec54115ead86e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113225_e6111d249769c480546ec54115ead86e.JPG&h=565a8aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113227_5d4849d0ae2ade5d330d4aebe43f0ddd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113227_5d4849d0ae2ade5d330d4aebe43f0ddd.JPG&h=a7ecb808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113229_bfbab0c3f9a3fd5e1bcbff46fa8907b0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113229_bfbab0c3f9a3fd5e1bcbff46fa8907b0.JPG&h=e5cf3736&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddd1ff4da0aec36d77c2db7d292c0246de17c31a","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f2db7780aed0bb303c8a509e66a462ce297ee7","tid":714824,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"值得一講係，現時呢度既物價對港紙係偏低，物價大約係港紙1／4，好似晚餐一個手抓飯大約hkd＄30，一杯咖啡大約hkd＄16。<br />\n<br />\n咁都叫 四分一 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"咖啡可能係錯誤例子啦<br />\n<br />\n但一個full course俄菜晚餐大約hkd100，係香港冇可能有，soho到要4／5百上落<br />\n<br />\n而呢度市內搭的士大約500tenge （hkd12）"},{"pid":"c969fc3822c5d9fb1966cb2b158462f7061bd76a","tid":714824,"uid":65933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a1a7377d68f97f9ee12bd6d21e75cb4d07e6bff8","tid":714824,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113704_8a9d8e53c944cc807533536183d82a8d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113704_8a9d8e53c944cc807533536183d82a8d.JPG&h=1261e193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113706_4a7ae02331292856d3a30ae072f3eee3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113706_4a7ae02331292856d3a30ae072f3eee3.JPG&h=43def725&s={SIZE}\" /> 清真寺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113741_48c81f087575a85ab101ba55416fb051.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113741_48c81f087575a85ab101ba55416fb051.JPG&h=6854e1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113743_44531957e2968943191aade7201f7305.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113743_44531957e2968943191aade7201f7305.JPG&h=18910646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老遠見到駱駝我就狗衝左過去，咁岩佢係到辦大事，小主人係到做執屎官（原來駱駝屎都幾大粒，成粒牛丸咁大）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113820_7e804e0f018f78138df17903e5f6602d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113820_7e804e0f018f78138df17903e5f6602d.JPG&h=940be434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113821_75b2c5e8608b0724aa06ee6566719793.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113821_75b2c5e8608b0724aa06ee6566719793.JPG&h=0a479301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太熱，返左去買條雪條解熱，包裝幾懷舊同似澳門禮記，好好食奶味好重<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113943_396fa6a4035849faf65e58b92fb878b5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113943_396fa6a4035849faf65e58b92fb878b5.JPG&h=5d8b378e&s={SIZE}\" /> 途中一路偷望民居<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113945_547cdf46c91c4aecd1a2f52cda475109.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113945_547cdf46c91c4aecd1a2f52cda475109.JPG&h=c620c86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113946_4c2c49ca4d7544589889e7d0e127a219.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113946_4c2c49ca4d7544589889e7d0e127a219.JPG&h=5e7f2f0d&s={SIZE}\" /> 羊仔係到食垃圾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113947_eefc380db5be9d38cfc9fd98f2d4e455.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113947_eefc380db5be9d38cfc9fd98f2d4e455.JPG&h=8e348743&s={SIZE}\" /> 似乎養駱駝係呢度係件好普通既事<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113949_5d596e8bb72f6d3ce1a9a41ce52dc8a9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113949_5d596e8bb72f6d3ce1a9a41ce52dc8a9.JPG&h=e96cc57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113950_a017c2d91dac52db00b78ca36af87d9f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113950_a017c2d91dac52db00b78ca36af87d9f.JPG&h=6e706aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113952_07e1f24c56d83ca6753d6c765c45ac32.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113952_07e1f24c56d83ca6753d6c765c45ac32.JPG&h=c2d0c08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/113953_f110b7fb398c41a386bc398cfe29ecde.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F113953_f110b7fb398c41a386bc398cfe29ecde.JPG&h=b3a26b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後經過長長既car trip經Shmykent既小機埸返Almalty去做全程最重要既事，見我既哈薩克朋友，而我地一齊去左KOK TOBE(大慨似香港既Peak咁），呢到係要坐cable car上去，同樣地有個怪怪小公園，又係有怪怪機動遊戲同小動物（好多怪怪品種雞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114203_b8fefaee3d331432ae92daecee8b98d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114203_b8fefaee3d331432ae92daecee8b98d9.jpg&h=a95c9d89&s={SIZE}\" /> 第一次見白色孔雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114318_81e235166b8008f0190023a9000731d4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114318_81e235166b8008f0190023a9000731d4.JPG&h=85a1e971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114320_3e9c0574704561c01ccdde9522af2363.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114320_3e9c0574704561c01ccdde9522af2363.JPG&h=2e6dfe4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114321_3fd47a8f3813f91266dfce497aab5e94.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114321_3fd47a8f3813f91266dfce497aab5e94.JPG&h=88d3a313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114323_e3b1d6bf58560045801888b549468a6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114323_e3b1d6bf58560045801888b549468a6a.JPG&h=dba70914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114325_f333f9ac87f46381255eb43d0ca35ea8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114325_f333f9ac87f46381255eb43d0ca35ea8.JPG&h=8d26275c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋友千叮萬囑我要影呢個Beatles像，話好出名遊客必影佢地全城都好proud of，我問佢咁佢有冇聽過beatles，而佢話冇&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114342_44f9bab14eb30fb44380b3003ab775f2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114342_44f9bab14eb30fb44380b3003ab775f2.JPG&h=7557485c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋友推介我去當地既Art Meseum，冇太大期望下竟然有驚喜。發現呢到都有幾多中世紀歐洲油畫，朋友同我講係前蘇聯政府留低既。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114419_f03cbe0d42cff92e7653c4b0e3a4f670.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114419_f03cbe0d42cff92e7653c4b0e3a4f670.JPG&h=4546307f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/114420_0aa15056a2b0c63e665f1c1c396ea67c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F114420_0aa15056a2b0c63e665f1c1c396ea67c.JPG&h=1ca27d1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c400d3b79bcd17b2cdab55eb61bef18035906ad8","tid":714824,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46586a7e06ecc102b84356eb2faddc18c2406a83","tid":714824,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nd街市都幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a32f1bf73bb16c7d5ca1eb8fe4cb930b94ff54","tid":714824,"uid":185469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"好懷念呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我前幾年夏天都去過<br />\n巴打有冇去睇沙漠同峽谷<br />\n仲有個Kolsai Lake都勁靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121643_57ce6f7f235813d64460e317a5789ab1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121643_57ce6f7f235813d64460e317a5789ab1.png&h=59b3f401&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121644_8455e3c7d872c3bdb0502a761c27898a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121644_8455e3c7d872c3bdb0502a761c27898a.png&h=735dbadd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121647_5101df79e313026d7646900fc71e92e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121647_5101df79e313026d7646900fc71e92e1.png&h=92b21286&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121648_296d625de272819a5f81f2cbac5c8355.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121648_296d625de272819a5f81f2cbac5c8355.png&h=d63442eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121649_618da2dc69085707bc73543d09bcb562.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121649_618da2dc69085707bc73543d09bcb562.png&h=89cfc310&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"622febd940c6064f2c3b5de8f24fd5bd634e4caa","tid":714824,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"8609f99d4015e092f89754972a02f34be06cb01c","tid":714824,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"係almaty green market 我食過成世食過最好食ge 麵，彈牙又爽到仆街"},{"pid":"6399083a2517ce45c7ff3c5d02efb2ee31e815c5","tid":714824,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"唔好爛想睇"},{"pid":"41b25bdbc4b9024227d65767a079c2eef1e4415c","tid":714824,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"你啲哈薩克朋友好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nShymkent 都已經話落後<br />\n100蚊港紙食一餐又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad006eaae281517420d16959db4ae863257ec4c7","tid":714824,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"dcf5d2f9a406bf5ceac7e35ec0879584f2fc3263","tid":714824,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"幾local <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0b92c91fbf0958d32b43e39a7dc9a716305893","tid":714824,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"